div2.p:
"Your uncle played you a nasty trick," interrupted Searles;
                        "getting married and then adding to the crime by dying. You
                        couldn't beat that for general spitefulness."

"She's come, sir," announced Antoine, emerging
                        from the darkness, and speaking under stress of deep emotion;
                        "madame the widow has arrived, sir!"

"It was dear of Mr. Bashford to provide a home for these people;
                        wasn't he really the kindest soul that ever lived?" she
                        said softly.
